@lilongabc you need to refresh or load the object to change the values of the stats. For example, here is code that I use in some of the ansible modules.

```
    def _wait_for_state_to_activate(self, resource):
        # Wait no more than half an hour
        for x in range(1, 180):
            resource.refresh()
            try:
                stats = resource.stats.load()
                attrs = stats.attrs
                if int(attrs['entries']['health.placement']['value']) == 1:
